Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H78&}安定区
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺走我双臂的青年不在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.73,0:03:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在似乎也出人头地了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许那时候我应该夺走你的惯用手臂才对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像对你的上司一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠原特等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿岩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平子 留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.12,0:03:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的人前去歼灭青铜树残党
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚门 你也去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要和你们一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是长官的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服从命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我与你们一起战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是那种不能平白牺牲的优秀人才
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候不要拖我们后腿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平子 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清楚自己的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位的库因克准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经穿上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然…呆在这种来路不明的组织里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我醒醒吧 笨蛋绚都
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然跟人类混在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们终究还是喰种啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和人类友好相处的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以忘掉自己是怪物的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你很幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是不成形的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就帮你拔掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是试作品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但「新」的防御性能还真优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果用的是十年前的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们早就要死两次了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们…赢了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们输了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3 4 5
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6 7 8 9
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 没有打中的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呗 你就那样把他按住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体都被打断飞出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还能恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经超越了喰种的治愈能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是惊人的生命力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃起来到底会是什么味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要追吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我们先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界是由力量决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量能决定一切事物的优劣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会输
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和老爸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿岩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿岩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原型可以执行到什么程度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要放手一搏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 「新」深入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由赫者制成的库因克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫者？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们能承受住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:07:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然性能非常惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我们也会被它吞噬…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠原
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经深入了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 这样下去就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是令人颤栗的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界总是充满掠夺和厮杀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们努力说服自己这是自然之理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们并没有理由夺去他人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掠夺生命的行为只能称之为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真的有灵魂存在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它好像并没有把力量借给你的意向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父…亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种状态下还想着老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经不在了啊 董香！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金…木？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的错 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…你要…笨…蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金木
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护好董香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,样子好像变化不少嘛 眼罩男
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你早就升天了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是董香唯一的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说你们安定区都是没胆量的废物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他…变得强大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多到时候了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于你的秘密 让我告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在青铜树到底想要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么可能明白！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 听我说完
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所珍视之物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很强大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才如果你想杀她的话 随时都能动手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绚都你不惜加入青铜树也想得到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.86,0:12:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野吕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个混蛋 把我放开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野吕 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西尾前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篠原先生 黑磐先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没事 平子和亚门先去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们分离「新」之后就去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会死掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 都怪我太没用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你…是金木的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说对了 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退 撤退 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上撤退 快点！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长 保护好董香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金木 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 金木
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西尾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点走吧 这里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会都死掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多多良
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得大概死了多少人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计200人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为了这200人 我们也得更努力地杀戮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 小黑 小白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的爱巢正在崩毁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 就算去找新的男人也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但请不要忘了我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近都没怎么去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也想着差不多该去露个脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑到最后的是我们「小丑」对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿岩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是陷阱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筱原
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得刚刚的那个枭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才也在战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤亡呢 伤亡情况怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生还者…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计只有一半
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去照顾店长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 回去之后想办法处理一下你那白发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以现在这幅模样在店里工作的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太显眼…这肯定不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,董香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会回安定区了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是…什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加入青桐树
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.91,0:24:14.58,tittle,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(645,610)}下回\N「舞花」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,op
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.11,0:01:22.83,OP-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}夢を見たんだよ　生まれた時のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:29.31,OP-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}美しで生きてね　子宮の町
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:32.68,OP-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我が手を叩いて笑ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:41.55,OP-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}絵の具を飲み干した　虹の色変わった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:45.76,OP-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}抱きしめられたくなった　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:50.56,OP-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}一人じゃ歩けなくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:55.15,OP-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}笑い合っていたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:59.95,OP-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}玩具に愛を捧げて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.06,0:02:09.60,OP-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}触れられざる子供達を  簡単な言葉で壊したい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:14.06,OP-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}娼婦が火を放った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:20.81,OP-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}遠くの街で誰かが死んだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.11,0:01:22.83,OP-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我做了一个梦 关于出生的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:29.31,OP-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}在子宫的城市中 要美丽地活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:32.68,OP-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}拍着我的手 欢快地大笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:41.55,OP-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}将颜料一饮而尽 彩虹的色彩悄然改变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:45.76,OP-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}突然想要被你紧紧拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:50.56,OP-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}独自一人要如何迈开步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:55.15,OP-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我们一同放声大笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:59.95,OP-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}把爱献给玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.06,0:02:09.60,OP-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}只想用简单的言语斥责 那些无法触碰的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:14.06,OP-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}娼妓放了一把火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:20.81,OP-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}是谁于远处的花街黯淡逝去
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.62,0:22:56.76,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}季節は次々死んでいく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.80,0:23:02.01,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}絶命の声が風になる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.23,0:23:08.08,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}色めく街の　酔えない男　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.56,0:23:12.81,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}月を見上げるのはここじゃ無粋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:19.05,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}僕が僕と呼ぶには不確かな　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:24.32,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}半透明な影が生きてる風だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.49,0:23:29.66,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}雨に歌えば　雲は割れるか　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.77,0:23:34.97,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}賑やかな夏の干涸びた命だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:44.14,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}拝啓　忌まわしき過去に告ぐ　絶縁の詩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:49.55,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}苦悩にまみれて　嘆き悲しみ　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.58,0:23:59.37,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}それでも途絶えぬ歌に　陽は射さずとも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.75,0:24:11.08,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}季節は次々生き返る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.62,0:22:56.76,ED-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}季节逐一凋零枯竭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.80,0:23:02.01,ED-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}绝命之声作风飘散
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.23,0:23:08.08,ED-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}繁华巷内 不醉之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.56,0:23:12.81,ED-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}抬头望月 不解风情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:19.05,ED-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我是否还能称自己为我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:24.32,ED-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}半透明的影子飘摆不定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.49,0:23:29.66,ED-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}若对雨高歌 能否划破天穹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.77,0:23:34.97,ED-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}以嘈杂盛夏中枯萎的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:44.14,ED-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}致令人忌惮的过去的绝缘之诗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:49.55,ED-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}满篇苦闷 诉说悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.58,0:23:59.37,ED-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}即便余音绕梁 也再无光明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.75,0:24:11.08,ED-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}季节逐一复返生机
